    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2e41632d1c5fdfcbc0478de3114f6d82.avif?t=1770057973\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎，车长同志！</h2><strong>《多炮塔神教》</strong>是一个稍微带点肉鸽要素的俯视角坦克射击游戏，你将在苏联校园成为车长，带领坦克社团的学生们进行坦克游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.poster.avif?t=1770057973\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.webm?t=1770057973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.mp4?t=1770057973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择车辆</h2>目前游戏中有超过100辆二战载具，你可以选择一辆作为出击载具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/59a1e9b034c89d09f21dd1e0abe2287a.poster.avif?t=1770057973\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/59a1e9b034c89d09f21dd1e0abe2287a.webm?t=1770057973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/59a1e9b034c89d09f21dd1e0abe2287a.mp4?t=1770057973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >改装车辆</h2>每辆坦克的炮塔是可随意拆卸的，在任务中还能获得其他车辆的炮塔装在自己身上，变得更强。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/189bb819e85c23f533b1d9f1e1704e40.poster.avif?t=1770057973\" width=600 height=30